                    </div>
                    <h3 class="feature-title">Instant Results</h3>
                    <p class="feature-desc">See your enhanced images in seconds with our fast processing technology. No waiting, no watermarks, no registration required.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <div class="footer-content">
                <div class="footer-column">
                    <h3>ImageEnhancer</h3>
                    <ul class="footer-links">
                        <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
